            <title>[PIG-337] If limit size exceeds number of records in the file, a few records get dropped</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-337</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Given a file with 10k records, the following script returned 9996 records:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a = load &apos;studenttab10k&apos;;&lt;br/&gt;
b = limit a 100000;&lt;br/&gt;
dump b;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like maybe the limit operator isn&apos;t returning its last record or something.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
